    			      MOVIE Plot

	The British discover that someone has perfected a way of
	tracking submerged submarines and is offering the technology
	to the highest bidder.
	An international crisis breaks when a Royal Navy Polaris submarine
	equipped with sixteen nuclear warheads disappears while on patrol.
	The British send agent James Bond to secure the tracking device
	and locate the missing vessel
	before its missiles are launched at the West.
